Available Tools: get_forecast_daily | get_forecast_hourly | get_forecast_weekly
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "location": "string", "days": number, "unit": "string" }
Response Schema: { "location": "string", "forecast": [{ "date": "string", "high": number, "low": number, "condition": "string" }] }
---
Question: What is the weather prediction for Rome over the next 4 days?
Call: { "func_call": "get_forecast_daily", "location": "Rome", "days": 4, "unit": "celsius" }
Response: { "location": "Rome", "forecast": [{ "date": "2023-11-01", "high": 18, "low": 12, "condition": "Sunny" }, { "date": "2023-11-02", "high": 17, "low": 11, "condition": "Partly Cloudy" }, { "date": "2023-11-03", "high": 16, "low": 10, "condition": "Rain" }, { "date": "2023-11-04", "high": 15, "low": 9, "condition": "Cloudy" }] }

